---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/logo-t.png" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://asanotakuya.com/news/yamanowa" />

    <title>山の和 | News | Takuya Asano</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Information for the spring gathering '山の和' at Jeenya in Akiu, Sendai."
    />

    <meta property="og:title" content="山の和 | News | Takuya Asano" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="Information for the spring gathering '山の和' at Jeenya in Akiu, Sendai."
    />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://asanotakuya.com/images/yamanowa-flyer.jpg" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://asanotakuya.com/news/yamanowa" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="article" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Takuya Asano" />

    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="山の和 | News | Takuya Asano" />
    <meta
      name="twitter:description"
      content="Information for the spring gathering '山の和' at Jeenya in Akiu, Sendai."
    />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://asanotakuya.com/images/yamanowa-flyer.jpg" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="news-entry">
      <a href="/news" class="back-link">← Back to News</a>

      <article class="news-article">
        <p class="news-date">2026.04.11</p>
        <h1>山の和</h1>

        <p class="news-intro-en">
          A live performance is scheduled for April 11, 2026.
        </p>

        <div class="news-body">
          <p>日程：2026年4月11日（土）</p>
          <p>時間：11:00 – 16:00</p>
          <p>会場：Jeenya（仙台市秋保町馬場字辺田86）</p>

          <br />

          <p>
            出店：<br />
            ミュゲ花屋／ペンギン文庫／bau leather／Roebling<br />
            ダモコーヒーハウス／cookie girl／本沢三丁目パン工房／Jeenya ほか
          </p>

          <br />

          <p>演奏：浅野託矢</p>
          <p>開始：14:00頃（約30–40分）</p>

          <br />

          <p>
            主催：
            <a
              href="https://www.instagram.com/jeenya7/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              @jeenya7
            </a>
          </p>

          <br />

          <p>
            備考：<br />
            雨天時は4月12日（日）へ順延<br />
            両日雨天の場合は内容を変更して開催
          </p>

          <br />

          <p>
            ※内容は変更となる場合があります。<br />
            最新情報は主催者の案内をご確認ください。
          </p>
        </div>

        <figure class="flyer">
          <img src="/images/yamanowa-flyer.jpg" alt="山の和 フライヤー" />
        </figure>

        <p class="news-note-en">
          Please refer to the organizer’s announcement for the latest information.
        </p>
      </article>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .news-entry {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 24px 120px;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    color: #333333;
    text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.72;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .news-article h1 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.12;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: #222222;
  }

  .news-date {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    color: #666666;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .news-intro-en {
    margin: 0 0 42px;
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: #333333;
  }

  .news-body p {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
    line-height: 1.65;
    letter-spacing: 0.008em;
    color: #333333;
  }

  .news-body a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.12em;
  }

  .flyer {
    margin: 56px auto 40px;
    max-width: 60%;
  }

  .flyer img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    opacity: 0.92;
  }

  .news-note-en {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: #555555;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .news-entry {
      padding: 56px 20px 96px;
    }

    .back-link {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .news-intro-en {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .flyer {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 44px auto 32px;
    }
  }
</style>
